perl-OpenGL
-------------------------------------------
Perl module to display 3D data using OpenGL, GLU, and GLUT.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.7.0-44
  libgcc1-4.3.2-2
  libGL1-7.2-10
  libGLU1-7.2-10
  libglut3-2.4.0-1
  libX11_6-1.2-10
  perl-5.10.0-5

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding devel packages)
  binutils-20080624-2
  cygport-0.9.6-1
  gcc4-core-4.3.2-2
  make-3.81-2

Canonical homepage:
  http://search.cpan.org/~bfree/OpenGL/

Canonical download:
  http://www.cpan.org/authors/id/B/BF/BFREE/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack perl-OpenGL-0.57-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./perl-OpenGL-0.57-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/perl-OpenGL-0.57-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/perl-OpenGL-0.57-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.10/i686-cygwin/OpenGL.pm
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.10/i686-cygwin/OpenGL.pod
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.10/i686-cygwin/OpenGL/Config.pm
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.10/i686-cygwin/auto/OpenGL/.packlist
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.10/i686-cygwin/auto/OpenGL/OpenGL.dll
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.10/i686-cygwin/auto/OpenGL/autosplit.ix
  /usr/share/doc/perl-OpenGL/COPYRIGHT
  /usr/share/doc/perl-OpenGL/README
  /usr/share/doc/perl-OpenGL/TODO
  /usr/share/man/man3/OpenGL.3pm.gz

------------------

